      "description": "An\u00e1lisis profundo de m\u00e9tricas. { scope:'adsets'|'ads'|'breakdown', date_preset?, campaign_id?, breakdown?, level? }."
    },
    {
      "function_name": "metaAdsReadAds",
      "description": "LEE el contenido de anuncios. { campaign_id } | { adset_id } | { ad_id }. Devuelve primary_text, headline, description, cta, link, image_url, image_hash, video_id. \u00dasalo para DUPLICAR."
    },
